src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"唔係喎！早幾年仲講緊<br />\n要不是中央政府照顧你們香港，完蛋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434c060ffe516d5bdc3fadead839d8cf04fbdeca","tid":1877764,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:48:44.000Z","msg":"18得唔得﹖"},{"pid":"7f81a8fb2047ec03bdc1912af89f72ec07e635a8","tid":1877764,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84758a97802c6cf697c4982495d9ad34accd48d8","tid":1877764,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"沙士後就靠自由行谷經濟<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎後呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"變法國"},{"pid":"308acab45a79c3bcc437b3bb130483a08a45069a","tid":1877764,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"樓市股市繼續gogo高"},{"pid":"b2189e080e3465f54a9e282af0e07ffcd4f70dab","tid":1877764,"uid":66547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:52:21.000Z","msg":"就算市道再慘,樓價都唔會再現SARS價,好慘"},{"pid":"7d19e6e85912ec16719ef71bc8d7e289a5c63f04","tid":1877764,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"人工減 物價加 樓價升 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871d544fd293514af20f1b16357ceb548b0282e6","tid":1877764,"uid":277363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:01:20.000Z","msg":"睇黎下任特首邊個做都仆硬街<br />\n攤屎越黎越臭，越黎越杰"},{"pid":"9a72ea1fcdc6b97ee0273a3b1c223b688f3e447d","tid":1877764,"uid":320135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"一日最衰都係佔中/反送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}